Mixmag & Anjunabeats Presents: Cream Ibiza Sunrise (2014) 

                   Trance, Melodic, Progressive, House | Mixmag  

                320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 05:49:47 | 390 Mb



What do you get when one of the world's greatest trance labels joins forces with the world's biggest club brand? You get 'Anjunabeats: Cream Ibiza Sunrise', out on Mixmag Records on December 8.It's a tried and tested blend of trance, progressive, house and electro featuring some of the biggest tunes from 2011, including Above & Beyond's 'Sun & Moon', Andain's 'Promises' and Mat Zo's' Superman'. Proving just how much talent is signed to the Anjunabeats label, there are other tracks from the likes of Arty, Andrew Bayer, Maor Levi and Boom Jinx.
